806
01:28:43,911 --> 01:28:45,401
No time?

807
01:28:45,880 --> 01:28:48,041
What's the time now?

808
01:28:48,583 --> 01:28:50,016
No watch

809
01:28:50,551 --> 01:28:53,987
See? Time's not an issue! Get him!

810
01:29:00,728 --> 01:29:02,992
Move, your woman is there!

811
01:29:08,102 --> 01:29:09,501
Get them!

812
01:29:15,576 --> 01:29:18,238
Stop! Stay there!

813
01:29:21,149 --> 01:29:22,639
Shit! Get them!

814
01:29:32,160 --> 01:29:33,650
This way!

815
01:29:38,065 --> 01:29:39,225
Over there!

816
01:29:39,834 --> 01:29:40,926
Stop!

817
01:29:45,373 --> 01:29:46,806
Hey, this way!

818
01:29:52,847 --> 01:29:55,782
Your woman is up there, come on!

819
01:32:07,148 --> 01:32:08,706
You want to dance?

820
01:33:25,326 --> 01:33:26,520
Stop the car!

821
01:33:31,165 --> 01:33:32,928
How dare you
make trouble in my territory?

822
01:33:33,968 --> 01:33:35,094
Sorry, Third Sister

823
01:33:35,302 --> 01:33:36,564
I didn't know it was your patch

824
01:33:37,271 --> 01:33:40,206
You didn't know? Where are you from?

825
01:33:40,474 --> 01:33:43,409
You don't know your way around
and come on so tough?

826
01:33:43,711 --> 01:33:46,578
Didn't your boss teach you anything?

827
01:33:47,148 --> 01:33:48,342
I've tried my best to learn the rules

828
01:33:48,482 --> 01:33:50,382
You've learned nothing!

829
01:33:50,518 --> 01:33:52,247
This boy is under my protection!

830
01:33:52,453 --> 01:33:54,785
- But the other one...
- I don't care who is him!

831
01:33:55,089 --> 01:33:57,785
I'll be responsible for this, understand?

832
01:34:00,428 --> 01:34:02,589
OK, no problem.

833
01:34:02,897 --> 01:34:05,866
After all, we're all in the same game

834
01:34:06,133 --> 01:34:09,125
When you have time, let's 'buddy up'

835
01:34:09,804 --> 01:34:11,704
Boss, you said that wrong!

836
01:34:12,940 --> 01:34:15,408
The one in the wrong
should do the red thing

837
01:34:15,609 --> 01:34:18,407
Boss, it's a red pocket!

838
01:34:20,548 --> 01:34:23,745
And invite the other to a banquet, right?

839
01:34:25,286 --> 01:34:27,880
Goddamn buffoon!

840
01:34:45,339 --> 01:34:46,806
What's your name?

841
01:34:47,975 --> 01:34:49,374
Nam

842
01:34:51,378 --> 01:34:53,437
Ah Nam...

843
01:34:59,754 --> 01:35:01,654
I'm going to buy cigarettes

844
01:35:52,740 --> 01:35:54,401
What is your name?

845
01:35:55,643 --> 01:35:56,940
Ah Nam...

846
01:35:57,077 --> 01:36:00,376
Ah Nam...

847
01:36:35,082 --> 01:36:37,016
If you do that, you'll be arrested

848
01:36:37,351 --> 01:36:39,080
Let me just finish this...

849
01:36:39,286 --> 01:36:40,253
Old man...

850
01:36:40,387 --> 01:36:42,287
You mustn't write there

851
01:36:42,489 --> 01:36:44,650
You're defacing government property,
I can arrest you for that

852
01:36:44,959 --> 01:36:46,859
Don't you know... who I am?

853
01:36:47,061 --> 01:36:48,085
I'm Emperor of Yaumatei!

854
01:36:48,362 --> 01:36:50,091
Sorry, Officer,
he doesn't know what he's doing

855
01:36:50,297 --> 01:36:51,628
Let's go home!

856
01:36:53,500 --> 01:36:55,491
Young man, wait...

857
01:37:00,374 --> 01:37:02,399
I've seen you somewhere before

858
01:37:04,111 --> 01:37:05,772
No...

859
01:37:06,480 --> 01:37:08,914
You were in a gang
and now you do social work?

860
01:37:09,984 --> 01:37:14,250
I look after Alzheimer's patients now

861
01:37:15,155 --> 01:37:16,622
Good for you

862
01:37:18,792 --> 01:37:20,225
First time I've seen you smile

863
01:37:20,728 --> 01:37:22,320
How often have you seen me?

864
01:37:23,631 --> 01:37:25,826
I've seen you on TV!

865
01:37:26,100 --> 01:37:28,568
- You're on TV every day!
- No...

866
01:37:28,702 --> 01:37:31,569
- I see you day and night.
- He...

867
01:37:31,772 --> 01:37:34,707
- I meet you at last!
- Goodbye!

868
01:37:38,746 --> 01:37:41,772
You've forgotten everything
except her face!

869
01:37:43,183 --> 01:37:45,242
Where are all the US dollars?

870
01:37:46,720 --> 01:37:49,245
I don't always... remember

871
01:37:49,523 --> 01:37:52,458
When I do remember, I get lost

872
01:37:52,927 --> 01:37:58,263
When I'm not lost, I'm too busy

873
01:37:58,465 --> 01:38:01,730
And since I don't have time...

874
01:38:02,169 --> 01:38:04,694
...I stop thinking about it

875
01:38:05,205 --> 01:38:07,901
Then I forget

876
01:38:08,342 --> 01:38:09,809
- I don't always remember.
- Go...

877
01:38:09,944 --> 01:38:11,343
This is the latest map of Hong Kong

878
01:38:11,478 --> 01:38:13,673
You point, I'll guide you there

879
01:38:14,882 --> 01:38:17,112
It's not an atlas!

880
01:38:19,119 --> 01:38:20,950
Stop fooling around!

881
01:38:21,155 --> 01:38:23,146
Or I won't tell you stories
over dinner tonight

882
01:38:23,857 --> 01:38:27,384
The story of Mountain Leopard
and Nine Dragons?

883
01:38:28,462 --> 01:38:31,192
The one about playing soccer
with Ronaldo when I was young...

884
01:38:32,266 --> 01:38:33,756
What about Beckham?

885
01:38:35,436 --> 01:38:37,666
Beckham, He...

886
01:38:37,805 --> 01:38:39,272
He plays rugby now

887
01:38:39,473 --> 01:38:41,065
What?!
